<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Text:ital@0;1&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Week 8 Day 1: We Won. Now What?</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f0;
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 4em;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: normal;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        
        header p {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            color: #3498db;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #34495e;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .framework-boxes {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 50px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }
        
        .framework-box {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        
        .framework-box:hover {
            background: #f5f5f0;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.15);
        }
        
        .course-theme {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 50px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 6px solid #3498db;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }
        
        .course-theme p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .strong-emphasis {
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .section-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 60px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }
        
        .section-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        .section-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.2);
        }
        
        .section-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: #34495e;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 4em;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .section-card:nth-child(1) .section-image {
            background: #3498db;
        }
        
        .section-card:nth-child(2) .section-image {
            background: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .section-card:nth-child(3) .section-image {
            background: #34495e;
        }
        
        .section-card:nth-child(4) .section-image {
            background: #3498db;
        }
        
        .section-content {
            padding: 25px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .section-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .section-content p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            flex-grow: 1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .btn-section {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .btn-section:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #bdc3c7;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        
        footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
            
            header p {
                font-size: 1.3em;
            }
            
            .section-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>We Won. Now What?</h1>
            <p>From Revolutionary Liberty to Constitutional Power</p>
            <p class="subtitle">HIST 101 • Week 8, Day 1</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="framework-boxes">
            <div class="framework-box">Revolution ≠ Government</div>
            <div class="framework-box">Independence ≠ Stability</div>
            <div class="framework-box">Liberty ≠ Order</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="course-theme">
            <p>Ideas matter — but they matter inside systems that are breaking. The Constitution is not born from philosophy alone. It is born from <span class="strong-emphasis">anxiety</span>, <span class="strong-emphasis">debt</span>, <span class="strong-emphasis">conflict</span>, and <span class="strong-emphasis">institutional failure</span>.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-image">📜</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h3>Section 1: Declaration Activity</h3>
                    <p>Explore why the Founders wrote the Declaration. Analyze grievances and test two competing historical interpretations—Bailyn's ideological view vs. Zinn's class-based analysis.</p>
                    <a href="section-1-declaration.html" class="btn-section">Begin Activity</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-image">⚙️</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h3>Section 2: Articles of Confederation</h3>
                    <p>Learn how the Founders created a weak national government—deliberately. Understand why they feared centralized power and what problems this created.</p>
                    <a href="section-2-articles.html" class="btn-section">Explore Articles</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-image">🏛️</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h3>Section 3: Audio Lecture</h3>
                    <p>Listen to an overview of how the Articles and state constitutions were designed to prevent the abuses listed in the Declaration.</p>
                    <a href="section-3-audio.html" class="btn-section">Listen & Reflect</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-image">🔍</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h3>Section 4: Document Comparison</h3>
                    <p>Compare the Declaration, Articles of Confederation, and state constitutions. Synthesize what you've learned and revisit the historical debate.</p>
                    <a href="section-4-comparison.html" class="btn-section">Compare & Analyze</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p><strong>HIST 101: Democratic Norms & the American Revolution</strong></p>
            <p>Week 8, Day 1: We Won. Now What? From Revolutionary Liberty to Constitutional Power</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
